            "is_major": false,
            "source": "Business Wire",
            "source_type": "news",
            "summary": "In Singapore, Cargill\u2019s Ocean Transportation business and top tanker shipping company Hafnia have teamed up to introduce Seascale Energy, a joint venture merging Cargill\u2019s bunker business Pure Marine Fuels and Hafnia\u2019s Bunker Alliance. This collaboration aims to revolutionize marine fuel procurement by leveraging the expertise of both firms to provide significant cost savings, enhanced transparency, and increased availability of sustainable fuel solutions. This partnership combines the resources of two key industry players and sets out to establish a new benchmark in the sector.",
